(1, 'index', 'Vastu Shastra, Vastu Consultancy, Vastu Tips - Seema Bhatia', 'unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book', 'Vastu Shastra', 'Seema Bhattia', '48320352e5_sub-mainbanner.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/meEdw7JYG0M?autoplay=1', '4ed4b7f171_home_banner.jpg', 'Vaastu Shastra is a science that maintains a positive flow of energy in the home by repelling and counteracting negative energies. ', 'Seema Bhattia comes from a prominent business family in Delhi and is a well-known name in the Vastu world.', 'Vastu Shastra, Vastu Consultancy', 'Vastu Shastra, Vastu Consultancy Vastu Shastra, Vastu Consultancy', '2022-01-29 11:25:33');

