(1, 1, 'vastu-for-bedroom', 'Vastu For Bedroom', 'Vastu For Bedroom', 'Let your bedroom be filled with love & positivity with Vastu', 'Make it Vastu Compliant ', '<p>A bedroom is a place of complete privacy and an abundance of relaxation. After the whole hectic day we just look forward to the bed, but have you ever felt discomfort or something weird in your bedroom? Or you are not able to get proper sleep? There might be something that you haven&rsquo;t noticed and this can be the placement in your room according to Vastu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The bedroom is the most important part of the home and we come here for proper sleep and a calm environment, hence it becomes imperative to have positivity round the clock. Here, Bedroom Vastu comes into role play. Generally, square or rectangular shapes are considered acceptable by Vastu for bedrooms.</p>\r\n', '138f59b9a7_Bedroomimage.jpg', '<p>According to Vastu, the bedroom door be open to a maximum of 90%, this helps to open a way to positivity into the room. If you are looking for the most comfortable and soothing sleep in your bedroom then keep your head facing south. Clean your room regularly and remove the excess clutter and keep the necessities only. Let nature imbibed in your bedroom with an abundance of natural light and air entering, making sure it has enough ventilation.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>You can sometimes change your fortunes by doing the smallest of things. You can boost the positive energy in your bedroom and even improve your relationship with your partner by modifying it according to Vastu Shastra.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>The above-mentioned few effortless remedies are provided for resolving Vastu dosha in the bedroom, however, in case you have more doubts and problems you should always seek the guidance of a Vastu expert.</p>\r\n', '', 'Remove the Vastu dosha in the bedroom', '', '<p>Avoid putting your bedroom in the northeast of the house or southeast of the house as the former may cause health problems and the latter may result in disagreements between partners. Transform your bedroom&rsquo;s energy ratios to positive with these simple points:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid placing a mirror or television in front of the bed. The reflection in a mirror should not be seen when in bed, as it may lead to domestic disputes.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Make your bedroom as positive as possible by choosing neutral or earthy shades. Don&#39;t paint the walls black that enhances the negative atmosphere.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>If your room has paintings with a temple, water, or a fountain in the bedroom, emotional outbursts are common to experience.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>An east-facing bedroom should have a bowl of sea salt or camphor crystals. It is recommended to remove any Vastu flaw with sea salt and camphor.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Bedroom – Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'If you’ve planned out to purchase a home in the coming year then check these facilities and services come along with it before making any vital decision.', '4ad372d8f1_bedroom.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/OdJAJ4bErIs', 'yes', 'yes', '2021-12-24 10:06:14'),
(5, 1, 'vastu-for-house', 'Vastu For House', 'Vastu For House', 'Enhance Positive Energy in Your Home with Vastu', 'Make Your Home Affluent', '<p>Our homes are the foundation for a positive mind, so it starts there. We all do our best to make the environment as positive as possible. Having the best in mind, our homes should be subdued, peaceful, and prosperous.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Vastu Shastra, a house is seen as a living being whose five elements, earth, fire, water, space, and air, are balanced to produce the most positive energy for the occupants. Harmony and happiness can only occur within a house that radiates the most pleasant and happy kind of energy. Ultimately, the energy of any home affects the mental health of its occupants.</p>\r\n', 'd2a653ba88_Houseimage.jpg', '<p>You may start and stay positive and pray, but that is just not enough for us. Do we always find something extra that will help us do to hit all our goals and attract positivity and harmony in life? The answer is Vastu. It can help rejuvenate your home by adding plenty of positive auras.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>There is truly no place like home where your mind, heart, body, and soul can all find peace. Complement your home with Vastu and bring immense peace to it.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Vastu Shastra considers a house to be a living soul that is balanced to produce the utmost amount of positive energy by balancing all five elements (earth, fire, water, space, and air). Harmony and happiness can only occur within a house that radiates the most pleasant and happy kind of energy. Ultimately, the energy of any home affects the mental health of its occupants.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu is Important for a Vigorous and Joyful Environment', '', '<p>Vastu sounds complicated and confusing to many. It is quite easy and simple to understand. Vastu Shastra can help you experience significant changes in your home when you follow these tips. Eventually, you will feel the effects of these when you bring them to fruition.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Keep your front door clean and well decorated so that wealth can flow into the house.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Cash lockers and almirahs where you keep cash should be situated on the South or South-West wall.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The position of the puja room affects peace and prosperity in the house.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Fix leaky faucets, taps, and faulty plumbing to avoid financial losses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', ' Vastu For House – Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Home - As per Vastu tips for new home, the main entry point of your house should face the north, east, or northeast direction.', '733f164e90_house.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-24 09:42:13'),
(6, 1, 'vastu-for-bathroom', 'Vastu For Bathroom', 'Vastu For Bathroom', 'Bathroom Vastu is Imperative for Healthy Living', 'Bring Abundance in your Home', '<p>In Vastu Shastra, there are specific recommendations for each area of the home, be it the children&#39;s bedroom, the meditation room, or the kitchen. Additionally, Vastu dictates where furniture should be placed at home not only for the direction of rooms. There are also Vastu guidelines and tips regarding the position and direction of bathrooms. Bathrooms are often not treated the same as a bedroom or living room, so they become a source of negative energy in a home. Anything neglected could become a serious issue.</p>\r\n', '3d8ac8130e_Bathroomimage.jpg', '<p><strong>Make your Bathroom Vastu Compliant with the simple tips.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The first thing to do is to purchase a wooden door for the bathroom of good quality. You may be adversely affected by a metal door because it fosters negativity.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Keep the bathroom door closed at all times to keep the negative energy at bay.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Fresh air and sunlight can be brought into the bathroom through the exhaust fan or the bathroom window facing east or northeast.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '<p>Having a bathroom or toilet that is not Vastu-compliant can cause financial problems, loss of wealth, stress, or even minor accidents for family members. You should follow the above-mentioned tips when building or remodeling your bathroom or rectifying its Vastu.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>We must place the toilet or bathroom according to Vastu whenever we build a toilet in our housing plot or purchase a home or apartment. Improper placement of the bathroom can be fatal. Below are the best places to place the bathroom according to Vastu.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>East of southeast (ESE)</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>South of the southwest (SSW)</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>West of the northwest (WNW)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vaastu remedies: How to clean the bathroom of negative energy?', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The bath and toilet spaces might benefit from a salty glass cup. Vastu defects are supposed to be eliminated by this method.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Take time to rejuvenate and care for yourself in your bathroom. In the toilet bowl, add a few drops of lemongrass oil to use aromatherapy to freshen the bathroom.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Clean and hygienize the area. Repair broken soap dispensers, toilet paper holders, etc. Replace worn-out towels regularly.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Vastu flaws can be minimized or removed by having a mirror on the exterior side of your bathroom door. But keep in mind that it should not reflect the bedroom or the entrance door.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Bathroom doors should not be adorned with ornamental statues or idols.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Bathroom – Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Bathroom - The bathroom must be in the north or north-west portion of your house. Do not build the bath area in the south direction', '6e1d577386_bathroom.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-24 09:52:50'),
(2, 1, 'vastu-for-dining-room', 'Vastu For Dining Room', 'Vastu For Dining Room', 'Vastu for Dining Room- A Well-Maintained Area for Eating Together', 'Eat and Laugh Together', '<p>In the whole day, I think the meals are the only time when the whole family sits together in the dining room especially during dinner, and enjoy the food with some giggles and gossip. This is something mandatory for the day to end on a good note. Everyone loves this kind of atmosphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you ever feel that despite your efforts, your family is having disagreements and fights during dinner even after you have tried so hard? If so, Vastu dosh may be at play.</p>\r\n', 'f42c5e1c7e_dinningroomimage.jpg', '<p>Dining rooms or areas occupy a unique position in Vastu shastra. The dining area features a table large enough for entertaining guests and family with food. Remember that the dining room is intimately connected to the family&#39;s health, harmony, and success. Vastu principles can be used to build a dining room that has been intended well and provides strength to the entire family.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vastu of the dining room places significance on the direction and position of the table since these factors directly affect the family&#39;s health. There should be enough light in the dining room and it should not be too dark. Creating a comfortable and inviting dining room will make mealtime more enjoyable. A bright and cheery painting around the dining area is recommended. You may want to try moving your dining table to the south, west, or even east side, or even adjacent to the kitchen.</p>\r\n', '5397429808_paraimage.png', '<p>A table with an irregular shape is not recommended. For a stable and consistent flow of positive energy, choose a square or rectangular dining table.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>As per Vastu&#39;s theory, fresh flowers and plants are also considered beneficial in the dining room and who doesn&rsquo;t like fresh flowers that immediately lift anyone&rsquo;s mood with their beauty and fragrance. The table can be adorned with flowers since they absorb all kinds of bad energy. You can also go for stone tables and Vastu believes stone tables provide stability because earth elements reflect them.</p>\r\n', '', 'Living and dining room Vastu Shastra do\'s and don\'ts', '', '<p>Considering the effects of energies present in the dining room, the importance of the dining room increases even more. We can maintain a positive energy flow in the dining room by applying Vastu Shastra principles.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The northeast section should not have any photos of ancestors.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>According to Vastu Shastra principles, wood is the best material for dining tables. Wood tables represent expansion and are the first choice for a dining table.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Mirrors are a good idea in the dining room, since they indicate abundance and double the food.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Dining Room – Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Dining Room - The dining room should be in continuation with the kitchen in the South, West or the East-side.', '52c75000bf_dinningroom.jpg', '', 'yes', 'no', '2022-01-24 10:19:27'),
(3, 1, 'vastu-for-balcony', 'Vastu For Balcony', 'Vastu For Balcony', 'Cast out all negativities from home with simple Balcony Vastu ', 'Sit out and relax in a healthy space', '<p>How peaceful and beautiful is it to start the day with an eye-catching view? That we all get from our balconies. It&#39;s always an amazing idea to have a balcony at home. Nowadays the demand for balconies has increased tremendously and they are considered to be a necessity for the people searching home. The balcony is also a special corner of the home, as it adds an extra element to the home.</p>\r\n', 'c6cb1fa91b_Balconyimage.jpg', '<p>But you might not be aware of the fact that with the beautiful balcony, it is also important to have it Vastu compliant. Yes, wrong orientation can cause major problems at home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vastu experts believe that balconies should be located in the North, East, or North-East of a house. Because this is the direction in which the sun shines most, it is an ideal direction. It is considered negative for balconies to face south or west. You should also keep your balcony floor lower than the floor of the main building.</p>\r\n', 'c52233ee10_paraimage.png', '<p>Vaastu principles are based on the logic of architecture and following them guarantees a durable, healthy, happy, prosperous, and peaceful environment.</p>\r\n', '', '<p><strong>Easy Tips For Vastu-Compliant Balcony</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Try keeping the balcony clean and clear all the time and avoid accumulating clutter. Clear is always better.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Well, the balcony being a place to sit and relax, it should have that positive vibe and for the same, it&#39;s best to paint balcony walls in cool, pastel colors.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>It is recommended that balconies should either be of square or rectangle shape. Other shapes are not recommended in Vastu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'A balcony can boost your house\'s energy', '', '<p>Having a balcony gives us constant access to clean fresh air, sunshine, and if it&#39;s designed according to Vastu principles, it will result in better results and positive energy. You should feel an abundance of peace and comfort as soon as you enter here. But, if there is a Vastu-dosh present, it will create troubles and difficulties. So, to prevent the Vastu-dosh, make sure your balcony is built in the right direction, and as such, it is a good replacement for an open space in your home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Following the Vastu experts&#39; suggestions for your balcony will help you to bring positive energy into your home.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Balcony – Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips  For Balcony - Vastu experts say that the balcony at home should be situated in the North, East or North-East direction.', '7c0fbf9d97_balcony.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-01-24 10:19:27'),
(7, 1, 'vastu-for-kids-room', 'Vastu For Kids Room', 'Vastu For Kids Room', 'Vastu Shastra- Usher virtuous vibes into the kid\'s room ', 'Energize Your Kids Room Aura ', '<p>There is no purer soul on this living earth than a child made with the purest heart. They exude warmth, love, and positive energy. Since they are special, it is important to have their rooms also be special. Every one of us is witnessing the phenomenal creativity in the kid&rsquo;s room. With the eye-catching and innovative items in their rooms, it is also imperative that it reflects a fostering atmosphere as well and this can be added with Vastu.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Children&#39;s bedrooms serve a variety of purposes, unlike regular bedrooms. The room can be used as a study or as a playroom with toys and board games. It must also be a resting and recollecting place. There is a great deal of time spent in this room by children doing different activities. Therefore, it should be planned following Vastu to improve your child&#39;s growth and overall health. This can help improve their study, concentration, health, mood, etc.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>It is recommended for a child&#39;s room to face northeast because this is the direction associated with intelligence, power, and strength, thus helping incomplete growth.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>We all need a sense of belonging, care, and connection to our families and homes. To foster this sense of connectedness within the family, it is crucial to create personal space for every individual, especially for children, and build it positively with Vastu. Integrating Vastu into their rooms will help to ensure their wellbeing and health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Following Are Important Vastu Tips For Children&#39;s Bedrooms-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The Vastu of kids&#39; rooms indicates that east-facing rooms are the best</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Your kid&#39;s bedroom should have a surplus of natural light to promote Vastu</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>There should not be open shelves stacked high with books in the study area.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'As per Vastu, clutter in a kid\'s room is a big no-no. ', '', '<p>Every child is born with eternal potential and talent. We just have to provide the right environment for them to blossom. A Vastu-compliant bedroom can be of great assistance in this regard. Just avoid these few things:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The study area should be clear of items such as old books, empty packets, shavings from pencils, and pens without refills.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>It makes sense to get rid of old broken toys before they pile up.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Incorporating too many gadgets into a child&#39;s room could create constant distractions.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Children should also be discouraged from eating while lying on their beds because this could lead to nightmares.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Kids Room - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Kids Room - A kids room direction should be northeast direction because this direction is related to intelligence, strength and power', '5785ff8324_kidsroom.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-24 10:07:18'),
(8, 1, 'vastu-for-kitchen', 'Vastu For Kitchen', 'Vastu For Kitchen', 'Vastu for Kitchen: Simple, Unpretentious, and Very Effective', 'Vastu for Kitchen- Is it Important? ', '<p>In Indian households, the kitchen serves as the source of energy throughout the day. A kitchen is believed to be one of the best places for better health, wealth, and motivation. Everything over here has its importance and its placement can affect you in different ways. Color, furniture, appliances everything has a role-play and its imbalance can create problems. This is why each corner and thing of the kitchen should be Vastu compliant.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Vastu suggests that the kitchen be positioned in the southeast direction with the lord of fire, Agni, which means it should be there. Drinking water should always be available in the northeast corner, but all burners and stoves must face south. You should put the bedroom as far away as possible from the kitchen since their energies are drastically different. Every appliance in your kitchen is important, and if it is positioned in line with Vastu principles, positive aspects of your kitchen will be accentuated.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>According to Vastu Shastra, your kitchen should be filled with positive vibrations, balancing the elements of earth, sky, air, fire, and water. Boost positive energy in your home by changing or amending certain areas in your kitchen.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>When designing a kitchen with Vastu guidelines in mind, one needs to consider the following important factors:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid creating misunderstandings between family and couples by never placing the washbasins and cooktops, which contain gas burners and ovens, on the same platform.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>To prosper in terms of wealth and health, it is best to place your sink, pipes, and kitchen drain in the north or northeast.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>To defeat obstacles in life, it is recommended that you put your refrigerator in the southwest direction. In addition, the kitchen will be more peaceful with this placement.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Grain and other stock should be stored in the southwest corner of the kitchen since that brings good luck and prosperity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Don’ts for Kitchen: Avoid any hassle ', '', '<p>Food is prepared in the kitchen, and food provides energy for us. When the energy from your kitchen is balanced, you can carry out all your daily tasks, but what happens when it is unbalanced? Wouldn&#39;t this create negative energy in you? To not create a mess, avoid some points mentioned below.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The kitchen should not be located directly above or below the prayer room, toilet, or bedroom.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The main door of the kitchen should not be placed on the south wall; it should be placed on the north, east, or west walls.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The kitchen should never have black walls and floors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Kitchen - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Kitchen - South-east is the best direction for kitchens. But if you can\'t find a suitable place in that corner then northwest direction works', '1edaa92449_kitchen.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/meEdw7JYG0M', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-24 10:16:00'),
(9, 1, 'vastu-for-pooja-room', 'Vastu For Pooja Room', 'Vastu For Pooja Room', 'Creating a Vastu-friendly Pooja room?', 'An oasis of calmness and positivity', '<p>One of the most auspicious and important rooms in any house is the Pooja room. Pooja rooms serve as engines that drive energies throughout the house and help them to circulate. Special attention should be paid to the design and placement of the Pooja room. You might keep numerous decoration items there and it might be very beautiful but it has a strong connection with Vastu. Vastu guidelines will make it have a more pacifist aura when made according to them.</p>\r\n', 'a12f8f6e8f_pujaroomimage.jpg', '<p>Vastu Shastra lays out the foundations for building the pooja rooms in our houses. According to Vastu, the northeast corner of your house is the best and most fortunate location for your Pooja room. It plays an important role in Indian homes, and they must be arranged in a sacred manner to attract positive energies.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>As pooja rooms are the focus of positive energy, it is recommended to use Vastu for them. Arranging things as per Vastu rules is the best way to go. Pooja Room Cleanliness- It&#39;s imperative to maintain</p>\r\n', '', '<p><strong>You should take into consideration the direction, colors, design, and materials when planning your pooja room according to Vastu.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>When offering prayers, make sure you face north or east.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>If you live in a north or east-facing apartment, you should ally your pooja room north-east, east, or north.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The doors and windows of the pooja room should face north or east.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Doorways to pooja rooms should ideally have two wooden shutters.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'What not to be done in Pooja Room?', '', '<p>Do not leave any broken idols or torn photographs in your pooja space, and keep it clean. Food should be removed after some time offered during prayers and bhajans, and the area should be cleaned with a wet cloth if it was.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pooja spaces should not be used for any other purposes or to store additional household goods. Ensure that they are always dirt and clutter-free. The pooja room should have a natural light source; however, if that is not possible, ensure it is well illuminated with LED lighting and diyas. More brightness, more calmness, and happiness.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Pooja Rom - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Pooja Rom - According to Vastu principles, the north-east is the divine direction and you must place your pooja room in this direction', '778bd1bec9_Poojaroompsd.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-24 10:27:55'),
(10, 1, 'vastu-for-doors', 'Vastu For Doors', 'Vastu For Doors', 'Exert a stronger influence in a house following Vastu Guide for Doors ', 'Place in the suited direction', '<p>According to Vastu, you should consider your main door not just your entrance, but also your gateway to the universe, where good energies will flow into your home. It is viewed as the transitional area, connecting the inside to the outside. Vastu indicates that the direction of the door is how good fortune and happiness enter the home. There is nothing more beautiful than a traditional decorated front door. It will brighten up your home.</p>\r\n', 'f03f0827e2_VastuforDoorsimage.jpg', '<p>Choosing the right door direction, material and things according to Vastu</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Traditionally, the main door should always face northeast, north, east, or west, as these directions are considered auspicious.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>South and southwest gates can be rectified using lead helixes and lead metal pyramids; the northwest gate with a brass pyramid &amp; brass helix, while the southeast gate can be rectified using a copper helix.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>You should avoid blocking the main entrance with plants, statues, poles, etc. As a result, positive energy is restricted.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Choose the good material for your doors, preferably teakwood since it brings good luck. The main door should not be made of neem wood or have metal frames, which is considered unlucky.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '<p>The main door is very prosperous with its two shutters on the inside and clockwise. Always paint and design the main door with beautiful patterns.</p>\r\n', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>It is not advisable to open the main gate to a house facing another from the outside. Inauspicious doors are said to usher in negative energies.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>It is always advisable to construct a door so that it is not centered on a wall. Do not, however, place the door in an extreme corner.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Make sure your doors open and close smoothly without creaking, and that the hinges are well oiled. As soon as possible, replace cracked doors to prevent arguments.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Direction is imperative part of Vastu ', '', '<p>Positioning your doors to let in the most amounts of air, light, and energy is extremely important, as well as preventing negative energies from entering your house. To bring prosperity to your home, embellish your main entrance door with deities and goddesses. To create a feeling of happiness and contentment, they should therefore be placed in the right positions to facilitate the flow and circulation of positive vibes. When planning or designing your new house, you must not forget these important points. The flow of Vastu energies in your house is influenced by these factors. Make sure you are just welcoming positivity.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Doors - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Doors - According to Vastu, your main door should be free of any obstructions such as plants, big trees, staircases, poles etc.', '8e7f1ce36f_door.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/mkmkhmo8Cx0', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-24 11:18:24'),
(11, 1, 'vastu-for-guest-room', 'Vastu For Guest Room', 'Vastu For Guest Room', 'Some Imperative Vastu Solutions for Guest Room ', 'Make the positive aura for Guests', '<p>We all have heard of the Sanskrit saying- &quot;Atithi Devo Bhava&quot; which tells us to treat our guests as if they are Gods. We all try to give the best to our guests and provide them with the maximum comfort possible. But sometimes without any bad intentions and fault, they might feel distressed or uneasy in your home guest room.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Have you ever thought about what can be the reason for the same?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There might be something you are missing according to Vastu Principles. Vastu Shastra is a traditional Indian building method. The construction and adjustment of the room should be to bring prosperity, success, popularity, peace, and money into your life.</p>\r\n', '0f7fb1706a_VastuforGuestroomimage.jpg', '<p>Many houses include a guest room to ensure the comfort and convenience of guests. This room is occupied by persons of diverse cultures and backgrounds, as well as individuals with different personalities and attitudes. In Vastu arranged rooms, negative vibrations can be avoided and positive energy can be created. When arranging your guest room, Vastu tips are a must.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The guest room should face the northwest direction. Additionally, the door should face the right direction according to Vastu.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The southeast zone of the house can also be used as a guest room.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Furniture and wardrobes should be oriented in the southwest, west, or south of a room.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>If the door of the bathroom is opposite the bed, it should not be that way.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '<p>Every problem on this planet has a solution, and everyone has the talent and opportunity to resolve a problem. If you are stuck anywhere, use Vastu to get rid of it. Vastu Shastra provides solutions to all the problems we encounter in our daily lives.</p>\r\n', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Build cabinets on the wall to the south or west of the room.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The South-eastern wall of the room is ideal for placing all electronic items, such as televisions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Don\'t do these things: Avoid all these placements for Guests Room', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>It is forbidden to make the guest room in the southwest zone</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The guest room at Northeast is also not suitable</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Guest rooms should not be built above basements or water bodies</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>When sleeping, do not place the guest&#39;s head in the north direction of the bed</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The bed should not have any beams above it</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>As important as other rooms in your home, your guest room should not be left behind. When it comes to the guest room, you should adhere to all the Vastu guidelines.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Guest Room - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Guest Room - The most ideal, appropriate and acceptable place to construct your guest room is in the North-West direction of the house.', 'ce9dddee9e_guestroom.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-25 04:12:10'),
(12, 1, 'vastu-for-study-room', 'Vastu For Study Room', 'Vastu For Study Room', 'Vastu Tips- Significant and Useful ', 'Vastu helping overall development', '<p>Parents often complain that their child is not performing well when they move schools, rooms, or houses, yet they fail to notice the change in directions that comes with each change. The environment in which a child studies and the direction he or she faces while studying determine a great deal of their performance. Not how much time they spend studying, but how well they concentrate and grasp information is what children need to develop. The study room should be in an environment that improves concentration levels and learning capacities.</p>\r\n', '567bcd8697_VastuforStudyimage.jpg', '<p><strong>Make sure it is placed in the right direction</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Vastu, the direction is crucial. This rule also applies to Vastu for kids&#39; rooms. Children&#39;s rooms should face east, northeast, or north. The room facing east means that the sun rises in the morning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sun is regarded as a powerful source of positive energy in Eastern holiness, so exposed children to its rays will become early risers as well as fill the room with energy. Children&#39;s rooms should face open spaces. Essentially, the idea here is not to limit sunlight or the view of the room.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>An ideal study room must be Vastu-compliant. This is a very straightforward process. Having your study room located according to Vastu shastra guidelines is the step towards making it Vastu compliant.</p>\r\n', '', '<p><strong>Tips to make home Vastu compliant</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first step is to determine the ideal place to build your study room. The West South West portion of your home is the best place to build your study room. The study room may however be made in the northeast corner or east part of the house if the west portion of the home is not feasible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reading and applying Vastu tips and guidelines is the second - and final - a step that you need to take to ensure that your study room is Vastu compliant.</p>\r\n', '', 'Some Important Tips to consider: ', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>You should always place the study room facing either east or west of your house; north is the second-best location.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>A wall on the north or east side of the room should display all of the child&#39;s certificates, trophies, and certificates.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Keep the door behind the study chair away from the chair. Attach the door to the wall.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>It is recommended that there is a small gap between the study table and the adjacent wall to allow for circulation.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The child can hang a motivating poster on the wall so he or she is not forced to stare at a blank wall.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Keeping clear quartz on the study table can improve concentration by making it more square or rectangular.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Study Room - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Study Room - The best location for the study room is in the Northeast, east or west side of the house.', '50ffd4b4d3_Studyroom.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-25 04:32:31'),
(13, 1, 'vastu-for-couple-bedroom', 'Vastu For Couple ', 'Vastu For Couple Bedroom', 'Get the blossoming relationship with essential vastu tips', 'Spark the Power of Love', '<p>A couple bedroom is one of the most important parts of homes. It is the place where two people connect and strengthen their relationship. Your age of marriage doesn&rsquo;t matter, what matters are the eternal bond and the love that you two share and for maintaining a healthier one, Vastu is important. The bedroom is the place to cut all the stress and difficulties of the day and live the moments of relief and love, for the same having room i.e. Vastu compliant is important avoiding different issues among the couple.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vastu for couple bedroom is imperative in building their relationship stronger and happier. But there are different things that one needs to consider according to Vastu for a couple bedrooms like bed, room direction, lights, mirrors, bed, etc. directly affecting their relationship.</p>\r\n', '60cf2dfd73_VastuforCoupleroomimage.jpg', '<p>Essential Points to be noted:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid placing any size or shape of the mirror in front of the bed or even at the side of the bed.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Keep the blossoming fresh flowers in the bedroom symbolizing the love, fragrance, and freshness of your relationship.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>North-east is not the right direction for couple bedroom as it is for pooja room, and it put detrimental effects on couple&#39;s married life.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>For a better understanding with your partner, you can choose light and bright colors for couple rooms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '<p>Vastu tips can surely boost your relationship with your partner but the main driving factors are the feelings and emotions of the two.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Wedding season is on and this season brings multiple changes and works with itself, out of which the most important one is getting the room of the couple ready. With the designing of your dresses, focus on the room essentials as well according to Vastu. This will help in bringing unlimited happiness to the house and the couple.</p>\r\n', '', 'The direction of the Bedroom is imperative.', '', '<p>Vastu is the science where the direction is of great importance. Each corner of the home is associated with it and similarly the couple bedroom, so accordingly, the couple bedroom should be in the North- Northwest (NNW) direction, avoid WNW, ESE &amp; SSW. It is not every time possible to adjust the direction of the room according to Vastu, and then make sure the bride&rsquo;s bed should be in a way that her head face south and feet face north.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mutual love and concern are the main parts of a healthy relationship but if it can be enhanced with the Vastu then what&rsquo;s the loss at it? If the love between the couple can be increased or your relationship can get more romantic, then following the tips becomes essential.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Couple Bedroom - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Couple Bedroom - A couple\'s bed should be either in the southwest or northwest direction of the house.', '6162822ecb_couplebedroom.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-25 04:45:10'),
(14, 1, 'vastu-colors-for-home', 'Vastu Colors For Home', 'Vastu Colors For Home', 'Colors in Home- Bringing abundance of happiness and cheerfulness ', 'Choose the perfect color palette', '<p>Can anything be considered beautiful without colors? Can you imagine how boring and mundane this world would be without colors? Well, that is something that should not be imagined, otherwise, it might affect us emotionally, mentally, and psychologically. It is for this reason that adding color to life, especially in the home, is so essential.</p>\r\n', '1b391427a0_VastuforHomecolorsimage.jpg', '<p>A person spends a lot of time at home and being able to balance everything in it is essential to leading a healthy and happy life, especially when it comes to the colors. But not every color is for everyone and every corner. According to Vastu, some specific colors are suitable for different corners of the home that can arouse idiosyncratic emotions in the people.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>During the construction of a home, Vastu plays an indispensable role in guiding us for different directions and corners to choose from. If the whole house is planned and painted according to Vastu&#39;s suggestions then it helps in boosting good, healthy, and happy living.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Let&rsquo;s know the colors for different corners of the house.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Living room: Having a broad and wide living space with serene white, yellow, or soothing blue or green paint makes the whole atmosphere extremely beautiful and peaceful. The combination of space with eye-soothing colors lets you feel calm and relaxed.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Dining room: After the whole hectic day looking forward to the meal together is only possible in the dining room and it is mandatory to have a peaceful aura in the room. According to Vastu, peach or the light shades of pink &amp; orange are perfectly enhancing the bond.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Kitchen: The place from where everyone gets their feed and the essential part of every home is the kitchen. According to Vastu, orange, saffron, yellow and red are perfect for the kitchen.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Pooja Room: The purest part of the home-standing for serenity and peace should be painted, light blue, or light green enhancing positive energy if built in northeast. These will be the perfect dash of colors to be chosen for the pooja room.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Bathroom: Vastu experts feel that the bathroom should have more colors like white, light, beige, and cream adding an abundance of positivity. The bathroom needs Vastu&#39;s attention to eliminating negativity from home.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Every color in your life has its own importance. ', '', '<p>Color is one of the most influential ways to balance the mind, body, and soul as it plays a prominent role in Vastu, the science of balance. Different shades of colors have different effects on the house and its residents. It is therefore important to choose the right color for all corners and directions.</p>\r\n', '', 'Vastu Colors For Home - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Colors Tips For Home – The room colour as per vastu could be a serene white, cheerful yellow, healing green or soothing blue.', '3f2cb4c859_colourforhome.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-25 05:52:25'),
(15, 1, 'vastu-for-basement', 'Vastu For Basement', 'Vastu For Basement', 'Avoiding Vastu tips for basement can cause serious issues ', 'Enhance positive vibes in home', '<p>Today, it is rare to see a residential construction without a basement in that it has become an integral part of every home. It is a basic requirement these days, and to prove it more beneficial Vastu has come up with different suggestions, and these need to be followed to eradicate negativity from the house that might occur because of an empty basement.</p>\r\n', 'f67243cfce_VastuforBasementimage.jpg', '<p>Some eminent Vastu guidelines eliminating the negativity of basement</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are some essential Vastu principles that one must follow to throw away the negativity and bring positivity at home. The following guidelines are essential for the basement:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The basement should be built in the north or the east direction of the house as these two directions have more space than the south and west.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The basement shouldn&rsquo;t be used for living or sleeping purposes, it should be used for storage or some gatherings.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>You can place the junk here in the south and west direction of the basement where its shape should be square. Avoid any ill shape for the basement as it can cause serious health issues and foreseeable losses.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Basements must have a minimum height of 9 feet and 1/4th of their area should be above ground.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '<p>Wrong planning of the basement and ignoring the tips from Vastu can ruin the whole atmosphere of the basement and can affect the aura of the home. It is highly recommended to follow the Vastu guidelines for bringing the best from it.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>People today need more space even if their homes have a lot of space, which is why basements are becoming more popular. It is an area with no direct sunlight and excessive humidity, resulting in negative effects. Adding auspiciousness to a house can be achieved by just paying attention to the things above, make sure you follow them all.</p>\r\n', '', 'Some Don’ts for Basement according to Vastu', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid building the basement only in the Southwest zone; it will bring health and financial losses.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid the construction of a basement at Brahmasthan- the center of premises.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid keeping heavy electrical and metallic items in the basement&rsquo;s Northeast direction.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid the dark colors in the basement instead paint it light with shades of cream, beige and yellow.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'Vastu For Basement - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Basement - Primarily basement should be built in Northern or eastern direction of house as according to Vastu principles.', '9a8f713bb9_basement.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-02-25 06:35:10');
INSERT INTO `vastus` (`id`, `category_id`, `url`, `name`, `heading_1`, `heading_2`, `short_post`, `first_para`, `first_para_image`, `second_para`, `second_para_image`, `third_para`, `third_para_image`, `fourth_para`, `fourth_para_image`, `fifth_para`, `fifth_para_image`, `sixth_para`, `sixth_para_image`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `listing_image`, `video_url`, `ping_on_home`, `mark_as_similar`, `created`) VALUES
(16, 1, 'vastu-for-patio', 'Vastu For Patio', 'Vastu For Patio', 'Vastu for Patio/Backyard- Healing and bringing positivity', 'Plan your fun gatherings in open & capacious Patio', '<p>In your opinion, what makes a perfect home? It&#39;s no secret that perfect home is a beautifully decorated house that has a spacious bedroom, a spacious living room, a fun-loving family, and each corner of the house is comfortable enough to be enjoyed by friends and family.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That sounds amazing, doesn&#39;t it? Constructors and developers aren&#39;t hard-pressed to build these kingdoms, and they can sure provide you with the best structures, but with the trend of high-end living, patios have also become a must-have.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p><strong>Having a backyard in the house is important! Why?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Creating a backyard in the home has become a necessity for many reasons. Let&rsquo;s see some of them</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Why leave extra space empty? It helps in covering it up.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>A perfect place for a small gathering with friends and family.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>You can enjoy the bonfire during winters making the space cozy and lively.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>You get enough space to wash and clean clothes and extra stuff.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, '<p>A backyard in the home has many other benefits, but with that comes the requirement for it to be Vastu-compliant.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p><strong>Let&rsquo;s have a look at some of the Vastu Tips for Backyard:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Location for the Backyard:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>According to Vastu, the best-preferred location is the northern and eastern sides of the house. These sides are more in contact with sunlight brightening up the day. West and South direction are considered inauspicious according to Vastu.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Items for the Backyard:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Vastu suggests placing a few items in the backyard that can bring abundance and harmony. These items are the five elements of nature that if not placed correctly can bring disharmony. Make sure you keep the area clean and clutter-free leaving no point for negativity.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Furniture for the Backyard:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>You can host parties and get-togethers in the backyard of your house if it&#39;s spacious, but where will the guests sit? I mean there is a complete need for furniture and the preferable one is wooden furniture giving beautiful look to the backyard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Avoid these things:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Avoid locating your house west or south if you want a beautiful backyard.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Don&#39;t let your backyard become cluttered, dirty, and messy as it will attract negativity inside your house.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, 'Why follow Vastu Shastra for Backyard?', NULL, '<p>Backyards are open spaces at the backside of buildings, and if they do not conform to Vastu principles, they can cause health problems and financial problems. The right construction of a backyard is crucial. The opulent design and the right emplacement of the backyard keep all negativity and problems away from the house. Construction according to Vastu shastra is essential for maintaining a healthy and happy environment.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'Vastu For Patio - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Patio - In order to increase the value of your property you must try to get the patio area constructed in between the east and north.', 'd8bd26dc45_door.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-03-01 07:19:54'),
(17, 1, 'vastu-for-staircase', 'Vastu For Staircase', 'Vastu For Staircase', 'Amazing Vastu tips for stairs- elevate your home peace', 'Vastu for Staircase- Get rid of extra troubles in your home', '<p>Each home is believed to possess a certain kind of energy, and Vastu helps determine what kind of energy it is releasing based on the situation of the family residing there. Whenever the home has positive vibes, it is obvious that members are happy and successful, and if there is any negativity there are often losses, disputes, and misunderstandings. This is where Vastu comes into play. It indicates that something is missing or incorrectly positioned which is causing the problem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In today&#39;s society, most homes have more than one floor and a staircase is necessary. We are constantly amazed at the innovative ways stairs are being designed. They are like the best examples of innovation. These might be very good-looking and attractive but are those stairs lucky for your house, your family, or you?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Staircases are available in a wide variety of materials and styles. Before you decide on the size, material, and direction of a staircase, you should ensure that it follows Vastu principles. You should try to build a staircase in the western or southern part of the house.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>Since Vastu dictates how to construct every aspect of your house, you also need to follow Vastu rules when constructing a staircase as well. There are several rules associated with staircase construction in the ancient Hindu architectural doctrine Vastu. In houses, staircase Vastu leads to a positive flow of energy in general, and in particular, leads to easy movement. Additionally, it decreases the likelihood of mishaps of any kind.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>Besides looking good, square and rectangle stairs are also practical in their design. In the case of both internal and external staircases, turns that are at right angles ensure good energy flow.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>Odd numbers are always better: A stairway should always have odd numbers (15, 17, 19, or 21) and the one never ending with zero. Exactly why? People usually put their right foot forward when climbing stairs. Users must place their right foot down at the end of the flight. The staircase must have an odd number of steps for this to be possible.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'Some basic principles:', NULL, '<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The stairway should always lead from the north or east to the west, starting from the north.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The stairs must always have an odd number and they cannot have a zero at the end.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Spiral staircases are not recommended since they are believed to be unhealthy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, 'Vastu For Staircase - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Staircase - The ideal direction to build a staircase as per Vastu is in the southeast or The southwest. Avoid constructing it in anywhere else', 'e455b75d5a_balcony.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-03-01 07:49:24'),
(18, 1, 'vastu-for-store-room', 'Vastu For Store Room', 'Vastu For Store Room', 'Store room can bring manifold changes in your life. ', 'Accumulate all of your stuff in a vastu complaint Store room ', '<p>Regardless of how big or spacious our homes are, we all need a corner in our homes where we can store the stuff we don&#39;t use every day. The right place to keep extra items is also important to make sure we can use them whenever we want a storeroom is a safe, stable place in which we can keep all our extra stuff. Storerooms are places where junk accumulates, so it is better to make them Vastu compliant to prevent the permanent accumulation of junk.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p><strong>Storerooms can be divided into two types:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Storeroom for food:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>All food items are kept here in this storeroom. Food items that are considered essential in case of emergency should be stored. Keeping extra food items in the kitchen becomes difficult, so there is a special place set aside for these items called the food storeroom.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Storeroom for Junk:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The junk storage room is another type of storage room where all the extra items of the house are stored. Decorative products are stored here as well as waste materials and furniture.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>In any case, it is clear that a storeroom plays an important role in the house, but constructing it improperly can result in serious losses and diseases for the household. Storerooms are places prone to negativity and evil energies, so people prefer to use Vastu Shastra to ensure their safety.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>Each and every small detail is important to keep in mind while making the store room vastu friendly like the best place to put a storeroom are northwest or southwest corners. Vastu suggests avoiding storing water in a storeroom. Storerooms should not have empty containers. Storage rooms are not recommended for sleeping, since they are unhealthy. A picture of Lord Vishnu, Trishul, and Swastik will make the room auspicious.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'Some imperative guidelines for storeroom', NULL, '<p>Make the store room of your house Vastu compliant following these guidelines. These will surely help you maintaining a balance in your home.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>In the Northwest, the zone can be placed food items, grains, household items, etc.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Three junk storerooms can be created in the east-southeast (ESE), south-southwest (SSW), or west-northwest (WNW) zones.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Storerooms should only have rectangular or square shapes.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>A door in this room can be built in either direction, north or east.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>A granary stock must be stored in the northwest (NW) zone annually.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Depending on where the storeroom is located, the colors used should be shades of light yellow, off-white, or light cream.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, 'Vastu For Store Room - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Store Room - According to Vastu Shastra, the right location for the storeroom is in the south-west or north-west corner to maintain peace.', 'b90831011d_VastuandColors.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-03-04 04:49:29'),
(19, 1, 'vastu-for-swimming-pool', 'Vastu For Swimming Pool', 'Vastu For Swimming Pool', 'Vastu and Swimming Pools: What Is Their Importance', 'Is it good to have a Swimming Pool according to Vastu? ', '<p>Nowadays, swimming pools make a style statement. Everyone looks forward to having a swimming pool at home. While swimming pools can be fun, they don&#39;t always suit every home because they&#39;re not made according to vastu principles. Vastu is an imperative part that one requires for making the home full of benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indeed, each part of our lives is intimately related to the way we decorate, design, manage and maintain our homes. As a result, people are not surprised when they want a swimming pool at their home.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>In many cases, builders do not give Vastu Shastra much consideration when planning and building swimming pools. If they are located in the wrong direction, swimming pools have a decisive water element it can attract misfortune and bad luck. For it to be most effective, it must be built in an area of balance between opposing energies.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>The luxury of having a swimming pool in the house is unquestionable. How to build a swimming pool is explained by Vastu, the ancient science of understanding. Always follow Vastu principles to succeed and be happy.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p><strong>Quick Vastu tips for Swimming pool</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>To have an fortunate location for a swimming pool, well or bore-well, the water tanks for them must always be placed underground in the North-East direction.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>There are only two places where water should flow: in the east it should flow to Ishan, and in the north it should flow to Ishan.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The corner of the northeast or the northeast side of your home will be the best place for you to place your pool, so it&#39;s best to place it toward the east or north of your home.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The placement or location of a swimming pool based on Vastu Shastra Tips is northeast to east direction and northeast to north direction, and then it indicates an inflow of good fortune in your life.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, 'Directions are imperative in Vastu. ', NULL, '<p>When building a swimming pool, it is crucial to ensure that it is built in the right direction and in the right place. Each of these factors is important in balancing the energies inside the home.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Swimming pool locations: The pool should be located in the northeastern direction</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Pools on upper floors: Not an ideal location for diverting attention away from a resident&#39;s home.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Swimming Pool Slope Direction: The slope inside a swimming pool should usually start from the Western side &amp; run east.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>L-shaped swimming pool: An L-shaped swimming pool offers shallow and deep areas and this shape is compatible</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, 'Vastu For Swimming Pool - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Swimming Pool - As per Vastu, Swimming pool should not have any connect with the south or western directions.', 'eae3a9e455_VastuandColors.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-03-04 04:57:50'),
(20, 1, 'vastu-for-servant-room', 'Vastu For Servant Room', 'Vastu For Servant Room', 'For healthy relations, make the servant room Vastu complaint  ', 'Use Vastu tips to keep your servants happy and in control', '<p>The importance of servants in our families cannot be overstated, especially in the modern era when we feel helpless without them. We all strive to find the perfect servant who will stay at home forever. There is a reason why people enjoy living in homes with servants&#39; quarters. However, the servant room should be built according to Vastu.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>Creating a servant room with the wrong direction or the wrong construction can change the mindset of a servant, which can lead him or her to commit wrong or ill deeds such as theft and usurping the owner&#39;s place. Ideally, the owner can control his servant if the room is oriented correctly according to Vastu.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>The best corner for the servant room must be chosen according to Vastu. If you want the good vibes from each corner of your home, you should set up every corner according to Vastu. You should avoid compromising on this factor and focus on finding the right solution.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>As a result, Vastu recommends that the servant&#39;s room be located as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>There is a belief that servant quarters would be ideal in the south-eastern corner of a house, as the servants would not usurp the owner&#39;s authority and would remain in control.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The North-west quadrant of North is another option for servant rooms. Place the servant rooms in this corner.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>According to Vastu, the northeast and southwest are bad places for servant rooms, since servants staying in these areas dominate their owners and sometimes steal from them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, 'Is it important to arrange a servant room according to Vastu?', NULL, '<p>It is recommended to place this crucial room in the right direction according to Vastu in the home. By doing so, the house will be filled with positivity. Owners will be able to control their staff better by doing so. When one does not follow Vastu principles and guidelines, small problems like theft, ego conflicts, control issues, illness for the maid, usurping the owner&#39;s place, etc. can arise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vastu dictates that the servant room should be located in the best area of the house. This is true! One should not neglect the servant&#39;s quarter, which is an important part of the house. In this place, the servant&#39;s mindset changes when Vastu is not aligned or when this place changes. This is why it is advisable to go ahead with servant room Vastu with this consideration in mind.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'Vastu For Servant Room - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Servant Room - According to Vastu Shastra, The best place of the servant room or quarter is the northwest zone.', 'c8d001fc3d_VastuandColors.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-03-04 06:18:12'),
(21, 1, 'vastu-for-windows', 'Vastu For Windows', 'Vastu For Windows', 'More positivity enters a home through wide windows.', 'Make the windows big and wide for plenty of air and sunlight.', '<p>To live a healthy and prosperous life, it is important to have a Vastu-compliant home. However, when building a Vastu-compliant home, it is imperative to make all corners applicable, including the windows. The location, the direction, and the material of the window should be taken into consideration since windows serve several purposes.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>The windows allow positive energy to enter the home as well as keep it ventilated. All windows should be of a proportionate height and symmetrical shape. A house should always have an even number of windows and always place them opposite doors. The sun&#39;s UV rays are most damaging when directed in the southwest direction for windows. North, east and north-east windows should be bigger than south, west and south-west windows.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>In addition to providing happiness and advancement to the family, the windows opposite the doors complete the positive cycle.</p>\r\n', NULL, '<p>Do&#39;s and Don&#39;ts</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Window placement is best in the east.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>The placement of windows is better in the northeast.</li>\r\n	<li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i>Window placement in the north is ideal and suitable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not believe anyone who says the number of windows doesn&#39;t matter, that you can add as many as you want. Make sure you get a good Vastu recommendation from an experienced Vastu consultant before making any decisions to enjoy a rich and joyful life.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'Where should we place our windows in our home?', NULL, '<p>There should be large and spacious windows on the northeast side of the wall facing the north. From the northeast side, air could be directed into the house toward the north side. Residents will appreciate the fresh air, sunlight, and daylight that flow through this window into the house. Energy is generated and related powers are developed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Long and wide windows are needed on the east wall facing northeast. This will allow air from the northeast to flow into the house from the east. This window lets air, light, and sunlight flow into the house, creating energy and a variety of other powers in the house.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Window placement in southwest directions should be avoided as it can cause the maximum level of harm to residents. Air, light, and radiation from this window are harmful to the residents. Windows play a valuable role in the house, the placement, size, and types of windows are all important.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'Vastu For Windows - Vastu Tips By Seema Bhattia', 'Vastu Tips For Windows - As per Vastu, Windows should be very large ones at East, North & Northeast sides. Windows should be medium ones at southeast corners', '1d7f7fe965_VastuandColors.jpg', '', 'yes', 'yes', '2022-03-04 06:22:31');

