(1, 'residential-vastu-expert', '1', 'Residential Vastu Expert', 'Residential Vastu Expert - Vastu for Home, Flat and Apartment', 'Residential Vastu is our forte. This service offers you solutions ranging from residential buildings, homes, flats and apartments.', 'Residential Vastu Expert', 'Vastu Tips For Residential Space', '7f124d3203_residentialvastu.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/meEdw7JYG0M?autoplay=1', 'adc558c470_banner-bg.jpg', '34e1b124c5_residential-merged.png', 'What a wonderful feeling it is to return home after a hectic day!', '<p>People and souls connect at home, which is more than a place of living or physical structure. Here is where we seek peace after a long day. You can only find inspiration, relaxation, and rejuvenation in this one place. Our home is where we spend most of our time. It is where we eat, sleep, and live together as a family. I think this place is very special, but sometimes there is something that has been overlooked that creates a mess or problem, and sometimes this even becomes too much.</p>\r\n		<div id=\"idOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\">\r\n		<p>We already know that we attempt to put good together and find the best accessories for home décor, but sometimes the accessories and the overall direction of the home are not suitable based on Vastu, resulting in arguments, stress, and more.</p>\r\n		<p>Nevertheless, Vastu has proved to be a good option to do up your home in a positive manner.</p>\r\n		<p><strong>In residential planning, Vastu is imperative.</strong> </p>\r\n		<p>Solar, cosmic, lunar, thermal, magnetic, light, and wind energies are all considered to be a part of Vastu shastra. It relates to placing and constructing objects or structures according to directions, magnitudes, and plans. Vastu must be utilized throughout the house to provide optimistic energy and vibe.</p>\r\n		<p>Being a place to live, a home expands our mental space and becomes an expression of who we are. Home design, decorating, and maintenance deeply affect every aspect of our lives. Vastu means dwelling, which is a place where humans and gods live together. Having residential Vastu correctly followed can bring great health, wealth, and happiness to the house and its members.</p>\r\n		<p>Peace, prosperity, and achievements can be upgraded by adjusting these energies. When a house is built based on these principles, its inhabitants enjoy happiness throughout their lives. It will be fraught with all kinds of problems, stresses, and there will be no peace if it is against Vastu principles. Residential Vastu encompasses several areas including Vastu for Bedroom, drawing room, dining room, kitchen, bathroom, basement, children room, doors, windows, and many more- each part and corner of the home. A Vastu-designed house will ensure happiness for all its inhabitants. There will be no trouble, stress, or worries in a Vastu-designed house. </p>\r\n		</div>', '2022-01-21 06:44:26'),
(2, 'commercial-vastu-expert', '2', 'Commercial Vastu Expert', 'Commercial Vastu - Vastu for Shop, Office & Business', 'In Commercial Vastu Shastra is considered just to ensure that Vastu has gained increasing popularity with the business industry over the years.', 'Commercial Vastu Expert', 'Vastu Tips For Commercial Space', 'd8aa68bf92_commercialvastu.jpg', '', 'e18825051d_dlf-plots-chennai-banner.webp', '36978609a7_listing_image.jpg', 'Vastu is essential for successful commercial space. ', 'As development accelerates and the population grows, small towns and cities are becoming metropolises. Population growth is resulting in increasing land scarcity for residential and commercial purposes. Consequently, multi-story buildings are being constructed for commercial activities, and their numbers are steadily increasing day by day. A growing number of businesses are opening showrooms and offices to market their products as production increases. As a result, commercial buildings have become essential.\r\n<p>Construction of commercial complexes is highly important in the present day, but it is equally important to follow Vastu principles when constructing. In commercial buildings, Vastu plays a significant role in the growth of office buildings. You are likely unaware of multiple factors contributing to hindrance in growth, disputes, losses, and other problems.</p>\r\n<p>As long as the Vaastu principles are followed when constructing a commercial complex, it gains fame and is sold quickly. Commercial complexes can then become profitable businesses or offices for owners.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Commercial Complex Vastu Consultation- each tip is important to follow. </strong></p>\r\n<p>Complexes are built to maximize every bit of available space, resulting in blunders occasionally. As compared to other ones, Vastu-made complexes are very successful and famous.</p><ul>\r\n  <li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i> Most of the building construction should take place on the southwest side of the area.	</li>\r\n  <li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i> Electrical equipment and generators should always be stored in the southeast corner.	</li>\r\n  <li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i> Buildings should always have a regular shape.	</li>\r\n  <li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i> Toilets should be built in the SSW, WNW, ESE, not the northeast.	</li>\r\n  <li><i class=\"fa-thin fa-hand-back-point-right\"></i> The north and east walls should have more windows than the south and west walls. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Known as a science-based architecture, Vastu Shastra employs reason and logic. It is important to build a business according to Vastu\'s tips for the office to ensure the well-being, happiness, and prosperity of all the employees. The negative and positive energies can be balanced by commercial Vastu tips. Choosing the best Vastu directions, layout, space arrangement, and principles of design can be done with some help from Vastu tips for offices.</p>\r\n', '2022-01-21 09:44:01'),
(3, 'industrial-vastu-expert', '3', 'Industrial Vastu Expert', 'Industrial Vastu - Vastu for Factory, Industry & Land', 'Vastu principles for an industry that can lead to more production, increased sales, no problems with labour and smooth working.', 'Industrial Vastu Expert', 'Vastu Tips For Industrial Vastu', '15ce3f0fac_Industrialvastu.jpg', 'Video Url', 'e6ade9ddca_dlf-plots-chennai-banner.webp', 'eb80f1c9af_listing_image.jpg', 'Increase your productivity & sales of your Industry with Industrial Vastu. ', '<p>Adulthood is incomplete without work. Besides satisfying the physical needs of people, it gives them an identity. </p>\r\n<p>Is it possible to survive without work? Are there cities without industries? Is it possible for a large population to survive without industries? The fact that industries should run flawlessly demonstrates the interdependence of people, work, and livelihood.</p>\r\n<p>Globalization and commercialization have led to a mounting number of production units in the country, giving a large number of individuals the potential to earn a decent living. You will surely recognize the presence of many production units that run smoothly and expand over time. This is not the case for every unit, however. Factory sheds often struggle with low productivity rates, poor production quality, and equipment breakdowns.</p>\r\n<p>With these increasing opportunities have come many challenges as well and one of the most challenging things is seeing the slow growth for a prolonged period of time without being able to identify the roots of it. Experts in industrial Vastu cite this as evidence of bad Vastu in the factory. It is clear that Vastu for factories has become extremely important these days.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vastu for the Industrial Sector: Follow for eminent growth.</strong> </p>\r\n<p>According to their nature, various Vastu principles apply to different types of industries. Without wasting any time, let\'s get started and learn some Vastu principles for industrial property right now:</p>\r\n<p>The Office\'s Main Entrance: Factory entrances are normally located in the third or fourth pada of either the North or East direction. Large, wide entrance gates are needed.</p>\r\n<p>Owner\'s Office Location: Building the factory owner\'s office is most suitable for the SW [South-West] zone.</p>\r\n<p>Machinery Location: Any factory cannot function without its machinery. Heavy equipment should be stored in the south or southwest.</p>\r\n<p>Electricity Equipment Location: The southeast zone is the zone of fire. For this reason, all heating equipment like generators and boilers should be located in the SE zone.</p>\r\n<p>Storage of finished goods: A factory\'s NW [North-West] and NNW zone can be used to store products to be processed for sale. This will ensure that your products are sold quickly.</p>\r\n<p>Washroom Location: WNW [West-Northwest], SSW [South-Southwest], or ESE [East-Southeast] are suitable for keeping washroom or waste.</p>\r\n', '2022-01-28 08:42:33'),
(4, 'numerology', '4', 'Numerology', 'Numerology', 'Numerology', 'Numerology', 'Numerology Expert', '8b45540c6c_numericalvastu.jpg', '', 'eef859dff9_Numerology.jpg', 'd3d2f9e3b1_Numerology.jpg', 'Numerology Expert', 'Numerology Expert', '2022-02-07 11:13:04');

